title: Number One
description: In the fifth emotional installment, our heroes go their separate ways and confront all their personal baggages.Once reaching captain level you think everything would be easier, right? No, the Consultant's four number one warriors finally track down our heroes and five massive fights ensues. Four number one ranking warriors, Pickles, master of ice, Brazza, master of lightning, Dakota, master of water and Isaac, master of ground, will our heroes make it out alive, or..?
author: Michael  Rogers
